        <num>41-2-3</num>
        <content>
          <p>A private nuisance may be abated upon filing of a petition by the person injured.</p>
          <p>(Orig. Code 1863, § 3999; Code 1868, § 4027; Code 1873, § 4098; Code 1882, § 4098; Civil Code 1895, § 4766; Civil Code 1910, § 5338; Code 1933, § 72-203; Ga. L. 1980, p. 620, § 3.)</p>
